Function Reference/comment link rss « WordPress Codex
-----------

Displays the [URL](/Glossary#URI_and_URL "Glossary") to an entry's
comments formatted for [RSS](/Glossary#RSS "Glossary"). Typically used
in the RSS comment feed template. This tag must be within [The
Loop](/The_Loop "The Loop"), or a comment loop.

This function has been depreciated, you might want to try
[get\_comment\_link()](/Function_Reference/get_comment_link "Function Reference/get comment link")
instead.

Usage
-----

`  <?php comment_link_rss(); ?> `

Example
-------

    <link><?php comment_link_rss() ?></link>

Parameters
----------

This tag has no parameters.

